// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// 5. RANK-UP REQUIREMENTS
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// A salt slot "ranks up" (RANK_N -> RANK_N+1) once its accumulated POW reaches PowerCAP(rank):
// N.js:11973-11977 (`_customEvent_RefineryStuff` handler) — each active cycle adds
// PowerPerCycle(rank) POW per completed cycle (gated by fuel availability via FuelCalc), capped at
// PowerCAP(rank); once POW >= PowerCAP(rank) the UI shows "RANK@UP" (N.js:11955) and a manual tap
// (N.js:11939-11943) increments Refinery[3+slot][1] (the rank counter) by 1 and resets POW to 0.
// There is no separate "level gate" beyond the fuel-availability chain baked into REFINERY_SALTS
// above (e.g. Refinery3 requires Refinery2 salt already produced) — no character-level or
// skill-level requirement was found gating rank-up itself.
